==Recording Audio==

To record audio  into [[Reaper]] do these things.

*Go to '''Reaper/Preferences''' menu and choose '''Audio/Devices''' and set the input signal input source.

[[File:Reaper audio options.png]]




Click the arm button for the track you wish to record to and check the input level of the signal. Then click the record button in the transport (image below).



